insights: Velocity has been relatively stable around 1.5-2.0 over recent sprints, with current sprint at 2.0
Team capacity varies significantly (31-50 engineer days) based on availability and team composition changes
Pricing API work has been a consistent theme across multiple sprints (W49-52, W47-48, W45-46, W43-44)
Sprint goals completion rate is mixed - some sprints have multiple TRUE goals, others have mostly FALSE
Recent JIRA activity shows focus on funnel improvements, navigation fixes, and quarantine system work
GitHub activity shows 16 open PRs for The Pets Table with work on portions, add-ons, and recipe selection
Team structure includes one 50% EM and one SE with reduced days, affecting overall capacity
Work allocation follows consistent pattern: 8 SPs KTLO, 25% tech debt, 50% main priorities, 25% QWs
Recent sprints show strong delivery: W49-52 delivered 72 SPs against 65 commitment (110% delivery)
